name: Alcina Dimitrescu [Resident Evil] Mini Dude #127
description: Countess Alcina Dimitrescu (オルチーナ・ドミトレスク oruchīna domitoresuku?), commonly referred to as Lady Dimitrescu, was a mutant human aristocrat. From the 1950s until her death in 2021, Dimitrescu maintained a pseudo-feudal rule over the peasantry near Castle Dimitrescu as one of the Four Lords of the region.
